{"tid":345390,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企網絡成日有啲不知名device","createTime":"2017-08-03T04:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T02:26:16.000Z","uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b83a847083fe5f2d17ea411c51c82cc5d663a1c1","tid":345390,"uid":48978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T04:49:45.000Z","msg":"幾個月前 買咗隻小米檯燈之後手痕連咗屋企wifi<br />\n之後成日見到啲屋企冇嘅 電話／tablet／電腦 喺個網絡彈咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一時見到nexus9 一時見到小米電話  明明全家都無人用<br />\n我已經reset咗隻檯燈 但係依家都間唔中見到佢哋彈出嚟<br />\n個wifi密碼唔係鳩set 所以應該唔會係隔離屋偷wifi掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nsorry個post有啲on9 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過有冇人知咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/03/124659_eee1cf5bda7e8feeaff02a137bf48f91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F03%2F124659_eee1cf5bda7e8feeaff02a137bf48f91.png&h=9d1eac99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n出緊post 嘅同時又有部屌米彈咗出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98564fb08cb4273a515ceb9d9bd07d78de7a813d","tid":345390,"uid":65774,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T04:53:40.000Z","msg":"用支那牌子抵你死"},{"pid":"e43ba70de210f2f60e5b00c378ab52a305d7f18d","tid":345390,"uid":80107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T04:55:42.000Z","msg":"Reset完檯燈有冇reset wifi密碼先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b8b52b1346ce35d352974cc1f8fb3720fc543a1","tid":345390,"uid":77571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T04:58:23.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"c16ff490a1e3a09f671e5d12103201485f829c08","tid":345390,"uid":86818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-03T05:10:35.000Z","msg":"你用